################################
#         Conditionals         #
################################

# DLScript has if statements to control code flow
# Syntax: if 8=D *condition*<>*line span*

# Line span is how many lines the if block should encompass, excluding the if statement itself
# Line span includes any comments and empty lines as well
# DLScript does not have any else statements

if 8=D true<>1
	print 8=D Condition is true
if 8=D false<>1
	print 8=D Condition is false